                    <h2>School Uniform</h2>
                    <p>Uniform is worn throughout the school and consists of clothing that is practical, lightweight and appropriate to the tropical climate. Pupils are also expected to buy T-shirts in House colours with the House logo.<br /><a href="school-uniforms.php"><button>Check required school uniforms...</button></a> </p>
